oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Videotaping audio - Chet Atkins and Friends - Nashville RCA Studio B - 1992-03-19
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Audio of a TV taping from the televised show Country Music Hall of Fame 25th Anniversary special broadcast in 1992. Taping took place at RCA Studio B on March 19, 1992 according to the tape container insert. Includes slate announcements, count offs and after performance comments and applause.
